## Summary
This documentation explains Amplitude's Data Access Control (DAC) feature, which allows Enterprise organizations to restrict access to sensitive data (PII, revenue, sensitive information) through permission groups, preventing unauthorized users from viewing restricted data in charts, cohorts, dashboards, and other analytics features while providing administrators with tools to manage classifications and permissions.

